Image 6 (marvel prototype)

Top bar star icon will be to add that current dish to favourites
Add a home button to top bar for easy access
Picture of dish with a rating embedded into the picture to show what that dish has been rated
Image icon will be the users profile who has uploaded that recipe - This will consist of their picture, about and some of their other recipe images
Brief description box underneath the picture of the dish
Ingredients box - Once clicked on this will expand and show all of the ingredients. Any ingredients that the user needs will be able to be added to the shopping list with ease and simplicity
Box below that will have the method for the recipe
Star rating system at the bottom of the page that the user can use to leave it a rating after making it
